name: core::net::ip_addr::Ipv6Addr::is_unicast_global
src:
pub const fn is_unicast_global(&self) -> bool {
        self.is_unicast()
            && !self.is_loopback()
            && !self.is_unicast_link_local()
            && !self.is_unique_local()
            && !self.is_unspecified()
            && !self.is_documentation()
            && !self.is_benchmarking()
    }
